        <briefdescription>
<para>Reads the PL efuse keys and stores them in the corresponding arrays in instance structure. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>InstancePtr</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Pointer to PL eFUSE instance.</para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
